replies.body:
Lets see no tanks, no supports, no ad assassins, no adc. All the champions you picked are highly aggressive. What if the player you are talking to does not have an aggressive play style. Basically your point came across repeatedly as play the champions I want you to play or don't carry out of bronze. 

A list of champions that can win trades and push its advantage well: every champion in the game when played properly.

Make up your mind. You tell him to play selfishly but tell him not to play Nasus. You specifically say that he will have to carry him self and play heavy carries and all around play for himself. So should he be a selfish player or should he not be?

You mentioned bruisers: {{champion:114}} {{champion:120}} {{champion:50}} {{champion:62}} {{champion:92}} {{champion:78}} 

Poke champion: {{champion:76}} 

Assassins: {{champion:7}} {{champion:55}} 

Burst mage:{{champion:1}} 

Not even all those champs are easy to play which is something you are an advocate for. You miss a huge amount of champion playstyles and even positions. If I were to guess I would say you are a bruiser main.
